==English==

===Pronunciation===
*bû(r)n, /bɜː(r)n/, /b3:(r)n/
*:'''Homophones''': [[Bern]]
*:[[Rhymes:English:-ɜː(r)n|Rhymes: -ɜː(r)n]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun|burn|burns}}

# A physical [[injury]] caused by [[heat]] or [[caustic]] [[chemical]]s
# The act of burning something.
#: ''They're doing a controlled '''burn''' of the fields.''
# Physical [[sensation]] in the [[muscle]]s following strenuous [[exercise]], caused by build-up of [[lactic acid]].
# {{scots}} A small [[river]].

